<!-- 列表/栏目页：ItemList 目录索引。numberOfItems 按真实条数填；数组项之间务必有逗号。放入 <head>，越靠前越好。 -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "ItemList",
  "name": "栏目页面标题",
  "url": "https://www.your-domain.com/category",
  "numberOfItems": 3,
  "itemListElement": [
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 1,
      "url": "https://www.your-domain.com/article-1.html"
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 2,
      "url": "https://www.your-domain.com/article-2.html"
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 3,
      "url": "https://www.your-domain.com/article-3.html"
    }
  ]
}
</script>
